node.text:
All good things must come to an end. It’s been an incredible journey watching KUWTK over the last 20 seasons. Through all their ups and downs, the one thing that has kept me glued to the screen is their evolving taste in interior design! Each family member has brought their own unique styles to the homes they have lived in. From @letthelordbewithyou Scott Disick and his minimalist modern farmhouse, to the gorgeously curated interiors of @khloekardashian and @kourtneykardash and of course the amazing homes of @kimkardashian and @krisjenner they have all offered a glimpse into their sanctuaries from the world.
I’m sure their design journey will not end even if the cameras have stopped rolling.

#keepingupwiththekardashians #interiordesigns #curatedinteriors
